upgrades.title: Harden Up
upgrades.description: Increases Overshield cap by 50%. Kills grant 50 shields.

upgrades.description: All restoration effects provided by Orb pickups increased by 25%.

upgrades.title: Tickshots
upgrades.description: Shots gain a 10% chance to fire a seeking projectile for each successful hit. Firing weapons reduces the chance by 5%.

upgrades.title: Dynamo Jump
upgrades.description: On landing from a bullet jump gain +50% Electricity Damage for 3s.

upgrades.title: Combo Wave
upgrades.description: Upon gaining 7x combo multiplier all melee attacks fire off waves of energy.

upgrades.title: Punchcard
upgrades.description: Add +1.5m punch through to primary weapons.

upgrades.title: Practiced Precision
upgrades.description: +20% Melee Critical Chance (x2 for Heavy Attacks).
